<div id="main_content">
	<h2>Huntington's Disease Breakthrough Equals Hope for Patients</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By Zenaida Kotala and Barbara Abney
		
		<span class="date">Feb. 22, 2011</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 345px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/2000/NE2438/en_US/345ella.jpg" height="226" width="345"  /> 
			
				<p class="photo_credit">Photo: Jacque Brund</p>
			
			<p>Professor Ella Bossy-Wetzel and her team have made a major breakthrough in the research of Huntington's disease. Her work will be the cover story of the journal Nature Medicine in March and appears online this week.</p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=00240041052a2b5bb012d4490764900278c">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
		</div>
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
		
			<div id="related">
